channel.description:
Title says it all. I have the common .bat errors in most delta clients. [code]
Read Error: modicon1 Read Error: modicon2 Read Error: membership Read Error: OWNER Read Error: hover1 Read Error: hover2 Read Error: chat1 Read Error: skull1 Read Error: multi1 Read Error: hovera1 Read Error: hoverb1 Read Error: hovera2 Read Error: orb1 Read Error: orb2 Read Error: orb3 Read Error: logout1 Read Error: logout2 Read Error: clanstone1 Read Error: mulit2 Read Error: hp1 Read Error: hp2 Read Error: hp3 Read Error: hp4 Read Error: hp5 Read Error: hp6 Read Error: hp7 Read Error: hp8 Read Error: hp9 Read Error: hpicon1 Read Error: hpicon2 Read Error: pray1 Read Error: pray2 Read Error: pray3 Read Error: pray4 Read Error: pray5 Read Error: pray6 Read Error: pray7 Read Error: pray8 Read Error: pray9 Read Error: prayicon1 Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/Magic/Pp 7.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/Magic/Pp 8.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/Magic/Pp 9.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/Magic/Pp 4.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/Magic/Pp 2.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/interface/custom 28.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2//Files/interface/clanchat/button 217.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/interface/custom 29.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/interface/custom 30.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/interface/welcome 1.png Read Error: C:/EPVP2/Files/interface/welcome 2.png [/code]

Switched all the paths to load from C:/EPVP2/ Not sure of the problem. Im just a fellow coder trying to learn, If you could help me that would be great.
